FBIS3-4513 "drchi062_a_94006" FBIS-CHI-94-062 Document Type:Daily Report 31 Mar 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Foreign Ministry Holds Weekly News Briefing New Zealand Speaker To Visit 3-10 Apr OW3103085594 Beijing XINHUA in English 0843 GMT 31 Mar 94 OW3103085594 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, March 31 (XINHUA) -- Peter Wilfred Tapsell, speaker of the House of Representatives of New Zealand, will pay a goodwill visit to China from April 3 to 10 at the invitation of the Standing Committee of the Chinese National People's Congress, announced a Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman here today.
